    <description>The "Mordor" Ultra-high Vacuum System is a sophisticated instrument suite named after Charon's Mordor Macula terrain, featuring a cryopumped 3-tier chamber, a 4K Janis helium cryostat, and various analytical components. Key features include a 6 MHz Quartz Crystal Microbalance, micro-capillary gas dosers, a far-ultraviolet monochromator with associated light sources and detectors, an FTIR spectrometer with multiple detector options, a fiber-coupled dual tungsten-halogen source, a range of spectral capabilities, and mass spectrometry tools including a quadrupole mass spectrometer and residual gas analyzer. Additionally, it includes an electron gun and an ion gun with electromagnetic filtering.</description>
